The president of the Bosnia and Herzegovina Olympic Committee: He firmly believes that China has the capacity to host the Winter Olympic Games successfully during this special period-Xinhua Net
Xinhua News Agency, Sarajevo, December 11th: The president of the Bosnia and Herzegovina Olympic Committee, Kvetschich, recently stated that the Bosnian side is looking forward to the Beijing Winter Olympics and firmly believes that China has the ability to host a successful Winter Olympics in this special period.
Recently, Chinese Ambassador to Bosnia and Herzegovina Ji Ping had a meeting with the President of the Bosnian Olympic Committee, Kvesic Kvesic, at the Sarajevo Olympic center.
At the meeting, Kvĕtkač appreciated the China-Bosnia ties and said that he had visited China during the 2008 Beijing Olympics and was deeply impressed by the excellent organization work. He was confident that China had the ability to organize the Winter Olympics in a special period. The Bosnian side looked forward to the Beijing Winter Olympics, and the Bosnian Olympic Committee was actively organizing for participation. The Bosnian side hoped to take this opportunity as an opportunity to expand exchanges and cooperation with the Chinese side in the field of sports.
Ji Ping stated that China and Bo have a special "Olympic bond."
The 1984 Sarajevo Winter Olympics were successfully held here, and in two months, the 2022 Beijing Winter Olympics will also open, presenting the world with a simple, safe, and wonderful spectacle.
I look forward to further exchanges and cooperation between the two countries in winter sports preparation and athlete training. The Chinese Embassy in Bosnia and Herzegovina will continue to play its role as a bridge and use the opportunity of the Beijing Winter Olympics to promote the deepening cultural exchanges between the two countries, and to make our two peoples “move forward together.” I also wish athletes of Bosnia and Herzegovina outstanding performances in Beijing.
Before the meeting, the Olympic Committee of Bosnia and Herzegovina held a “Tenth Annual Best Athlete” award ceremony and Ji Ping as the special guest presented an award to the best young athlete in Bosnia and Herzegovina.
The Beijing Winter Olympic promotional video is playing on a loop at the event site.
